title: Good Omens Animatic - Raising Warlock
author: Judgement Boy
comment: Okay but imagine a seven-year-old Warlock playing Undertale while Brother Francis and Nanny Astoreth encourage him to spare/slaughter everyone.
Can we all take a second to realize Crowley was his Nanny which means he raised Warlock for the most part. And Warlock is not dead. lol
I’M HERE TO SPREAD THE GOOD WORD; THE INEFFABLE HUSBANDS WILL RETURN IN A 2ND SEASON

Dude Warlock must’ve grown up to be such a weird guy. Constantly growing up with inconsistent morals must’ve been so weird for him but who the hell is gonna believe that his sadistic nanny and friendly gardener were telling him weirdly opposite things.
One little detail that I will forever appreciate is the fact that Nanny Ashtoreth and Brother Francis are on Warlock's left and right sides respectively
